data.title: Original Letters and Papers of The Late Viscount Strangford
data.meta_description: Original Letters and Papers of the Late Viscount Strangford   - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. The document appears to be a collection of letters, papers, and other documents related to Viscount Strangford and his work in philology and related fields. It includes an introduction by the editor, Viscountess Strangford, who notes that Lord Strangford wrote extensively on philology and related subjects in his letters and correspondence. The editor has collected some of these letters and papers for publication. It also includes a preface with praise for Lord Strangford's expertise and knowledge from multiple fields including history, politics, and linguistics. Additionally, it includes two letters of praise for Lord Strangford - one from Prince Lucien Bonaparte commending his work in philology, and another from Professor Arminius Vambery
